OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777964751
OL,3,COxford United Superfan completes
OL,4,Cwalking challenge after cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FA lifelong Oxford United Fan has
OL,8,Fraised more than #8,000 for charity
OL,9,Fafter walking 125 miles from the
OL,10,Fclub's Kassam Stadium to Millwall's
OL,11,Fhomeground, The Den for the team's
OL,12,Flast match of the season.
OL,14,FNeil McManus took on the challenge
OL,15,Fafter he was diagnosed with bladder
OL,16,Fcancer in a bid to raise awareness of
OL,17,Fthe symptoms of this type of cancer.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
