PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777964751
OL,3,COxford United Superfan completes
OL,4,Cwalking challenge after cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FThe U's superfan says thankfully it
OL,8,Fwas caught early and he was treated
OL,9,Fwithin a month. He is now back at work
OL,10,Fbut he wants to make sure others know
OL,11,Fwhat to look out for.
OL,13,FNeil is urging anyone who notices
OL,14,Fblood in their urine, or needing the
OL,15,Ftoilet more often, especially at
OL,16,Fnight, to get it checked.
OL,18,FNeil walked along the Thames Path for
OL,19,F5 days. In total he walked the
OL,20,Fdistance of 5 marathons.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
