OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1777964751
OL,3,COxford United Superfan completes
OL,4,Cwalking challenge after cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FAlong the way he's been joined by
OL,8,Ffriends and family and money raised
OL,9,Fwill go to Fight Bladder Cancer, a
OL,10,Fcharity based in Chinnor.
OL,12,FAlthough Oxford United's fate was
OL,13,Falready sealed before the game at
OL,14,FMillwall on Saturday, Neil was given a
OL,15,Fboost with some messages of support
OL,16,Ffrom some of the players.
OL,18,FMillwall beat Oxford United 2 - nil at
OL,19,Fthe weekend. Oxford United will be
OL,20,Frelegated from the Championship.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
